  "occasion": "Inauguration of the new auditorium by Governor of Maharashtra Dr Vijayalakshmi Pandit on 22 August 1963. The recording opens with speeches by Palghat Mani Iyer (00:00:44), TN Krishnan (00:06:12), Ariyakudi Ramanuja Iyengar (00:08:50), and institution-builder TV Ramanujam (00:13:07). The concert is the debut classical performance in the new hall. Chembai Vaidyanatha Bhagavatar performed the same evening; MS Subbulakshmi performed the following day.",
